## Catalog of artifacts

### 1. Operational protocol (this file)
Read first in any session that touches projects of [ORG_SLUG].

### 2. Governance documents (in `docs/governance/`)
- `document-control.md` — status matrix of all governance documents
- `canonical-sources-map.md` — what document is canonical for what topic
- `dns-governance-survey.md` — subdomain ownership and naming
- `lgpd-system-matrix.md` — LGPD compliance per system
- `naming-standards.md` — project, branch, environment naming conventions
- `retention-technical-annexes/` — per-app data retention rules

### 3. Architectural diagrams (in `docs/diagrams/`)
- `c4-context-ecosystem.drawio` — C4 Level 1 (organization-wide)
- `c4-containers-<app>.drawio` — C4 Level 2 per app
- `deployment-macro.drawio` — deployment topology
- `dfd-macro.drawio` — data flow
- `security-map-iso-lgpd.drawio` — security/compliance mapping

### 4. Applications (in `applications/`)
One folder per app. Each contains `README.md` describing the app's role,
hosts, key documents.

### 5. Hosts (in `hosts/`)
One folder per production host. Each contains `operational-state.md`
describing what runs there, ports, env vars, monitoring.

