## How this universe is maintained

Bootstrapped by `/rsct-init-universe` of the RSCT framework.
Subsequent `/rsct-setup` runs on projects of [ORG_SLUG] register their apps
under `applications/`.

Most artifacts (LGPD matrix, DNS survey, diagrams) require human curation —
the framework creates placeholders; you fill them as the organization grows.

To re-run the bootstrap (idempotent — preserves existing content):
